Using framework bootstrap

My database structure for comment:
1.ID 2. Content 3. Parent 4. Has_child.

ID is the primary attribute, 
parent -1 means root.
Has_child -1 means no child, 1 means has child.

the print_comment_rec function recursively prints out all the comment in database.

For pretection from injection attacks, I used the mysql_real_escape_string function.

For filter, I used the str_replace function.

Used Ajax to change iframe without reload the whole page.

Send quest to change_iframe.php when click the buttons.

URL: https://web.engr.illinois.edu/~pan30/